    <item>
      <title>伊朗、胡塞武装袭击后美国将斥资 12 亿美元补充武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pentagon-will-spend-1-2-billion-to-restock-munitions-fired-in-middle-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的预算文件，五角大楼将花费约 12 亿美元来维护部署在红海行动中的舰艇，并补充用于击退伊朗及其代理人袭击的导弹库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/pentagon-will-spend-1-2-billion-to-restock-munitions-fired-in-middle-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
